      <title>禽流感病毒袭击奶牛，令肉类和牛奶贸易商感到不安</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/spread-of-bird-flu-cases-in-cattle-herds-fuels-demand-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一种导致数百万只鸟类死亡的病毒正在美国奶牛中传播，引发人们对疫情爆发可能损害乳制品和牛肉需求的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/spread-of-bird-flu-cases-in-cattle-herds-fuels-demand-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 15:06:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
