      <title>警告 2022 年日元干预的前官员敲响了警钟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/ex-official-who-warned-of-2022-yen-intervention-sounds-new-alarm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本前货币主管表示，考虑到主要官员发出的高度警告，如果日元贬值超出当前区间，日本已准备好随时干预货币市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/ex-official-who-warned-of-2022-yen-intervention-sounds-new-alarm</guid>
